description:
I don't care what your tastes are, Teo is one extremely beautiful guy.
He's spent his teen years surrounded by hot guys with ripplin muscles, and one of his buddies shook him and said "Dude, you can't eat a cake every night for dinner!"
So he started hitting the gym hard and is still unsure about his new found physique, which I think is fantastic.
Teo has an amazing smile, and a fun "go for it!" attitude. He seems totally secure in the video, but I assure you, he was worried the entire time he wasn't gonna be liked by you all.
I guess what I am trying to say is, he wants YOU guys to think he is hot. He is eager to please you and wants to be your favorite guy on the site.
I think he could be too. He's just about one of the nicest sexiest guys I have met.
His best friend works for another big site, and I think Teo had so much fun, he is talking his buddy into coming down and doing a scene with him.
I am certain Teo will become one of your faves!
title: Teo - Solo
